I create **high-quality, unique business cards** that help you stand out and leave a memorable impression. Whether you need **modern, minimalist, or luxury designs**, Ill craft a business card that perfectly reflects your brand and personality.

With a focus solely on **business cards**, I ensure every design is tailored to your specific needs, providing print-ready files for hassle-free printing.

Lets design a business card that sets you apart. **Contact me now to get started and elevate your brand with a professional business card!**

Title: I will design outstanding business card design print ready
Description:
If you are looking for a modern business card design, this is the gig for you **(logo design is not included in this service).**

**Who am I?**

I'm Saad, a graphic designer based in London with a passion for creative problem-solving through minimal design. With over 7 years of experience, I've had the privilege of working with more than 3,500 clients worldwide, delivering impactful and thoughtful design solutions.

**What do I need to get started?**

* Your logo (preferably AI/EPS/SVG vector file)
* The details you want on the card

**Customise your business card with add-ons\*, we offer:**

* Raised Spot UV
* Foil Accent
* Letterpress
* Die-cut
* Iridescent Foil

\* Additional charges may apply.

**Other upgrades you might be interested in**

* Digital business card (clickable PDF)
* HTML Email Signature
* Letterhead (Docx Included)
* Presentation folder
* Envelopes
* Gift card
* Referral card / Appointment card
* Product insert

If you require an add-on that has not been listed, let me know and I will endeavour to accommodate your request.

**By default, the final files are optimised for Vistaprint.**

There will be extra charges for additional card variations, such as additional employee card files.
Basic_Description: 2x design options | 300 DPI CMYK | PDF/JPG files | 3x revision rounds on 1 selected design
